@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.description)VMware KVM runs virtual machines and allows switching among them and the host via a hot key.
Powers off the specified virtual machine.
Detaches from the specified VM, leaving it running in the background.
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.vmAuthFailed)Failed to authenticate to the virtual machine. Please check your password and try again.
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.powerOff.errorFmt)Failed to power off the virtual machine "%s": %s
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.powerOn.errorFmt)Failed to power on the virtual machine "%s": %s
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.updateCycleHotKey.errorFmt)Failed to update the cycle hot key. The old cycle hot key (%s) will remain in effect until VMware KVM is restarted.
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.updateCycleHotKey.error)Failed to update the cycle hot key.
vmkvm: Setting the cycle hot key to %s
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.usageHintFmt)Press %s to switch among virtual machines and the host.
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.registerCycleHotKey.error)Failed to register the cycle hot key. The hot key might already be in use. Try running "vmware-kvm.exe --preferences" and choosing a different hot key.
vmkvm: Failed to register the cycle hot-key.
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.App.OnVMOpenAbort.encryptedFmt)The virtual machine "%s" is encrypted. You must enter its password to continue.
vmkvm: Finished opening VM while not ready.
@&!*@*@(msg.player.login.captionFmt)Enter your user name and password for %s.
vmkvm: Rejecting IPC request: Invalid command.
vmkvm: Rejecting IPC request: Application is not initialized.
vmkvm: Rejecting IPC request: IPC is not allowed in the current state.
vmkvm: Failed to find MKS hooked key: %s
vmkvm: Creating %s UI frame on monitor %d (%s)
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.preferencesDialog.exitBehavior.leaveVMsRunning)&Leave virtual machines running in the background
@&!*@*@(msg.vmkvm.preferencesDialog.disallowedHotKeyFmt)%s is not an allowed hot key.
